
### This endpoint can be called to CREATE a savings account
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/account/
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
idempotency-key: 123456098765

{
  "branchCode": "1243",
  "accountType": "Savings",
  "customerNumber": "1755",
  "accountNickName": null
}

### This endpoint can be called to CREATE a customer
### This is an idempotent endpoint and can be called multiple times without creating multiple customers - the customer name will be updated to the most latest request
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/customer/
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerNumber": "1755",
  "customerName": {
    "firstName": "Angel",
    "lastName": "Klzad"
  }
}

